description: Join JACK FM and Richard Blade for a 80's Pool Party at Morongo Casino Resort & Spa all summer long!
maintext:
It’s Jack FM’s Summer Camp! We’re taking over the Oasis pool at Morongo Casino Resort & Spa featuring Richard Blade.
Catch him spinning live from 1pm-3pm on the following dates May 7th, May 14th, June 3rd, June 10th & June 25th.
Click here to purchase day passes to Oasis Pool!
title: 80’s Pool Party with Richard Blade
